                "tool_use_id": "tooluse_4Gr-p7pGRZC0wbXdDb4u8w",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "Json": {
                      "exit_status": "0",
                      "stdout": "commit 5aa281c487c7f797d3c8f4376069295242e9ba2e\nAuthor: Developer <user@example.com>\nDate:   Fri Nov 28 08:03:22 2025 +0800\n\n    refactor: optimize DesignerPanel architecture\n    \n    - Extract DesignerPanel static methods to DesignerPanelFactory\n    - Use DesignerService singleton for HmlController management\n    - Decouple MessageHandler from WebviewPanel\n    - Extract HTML generation to WebviewContentProvider\n    - Use EventEmitter for FileManager UI updates\n\n src/core/CommandManager.ts           |  1 +\n src/designer/DesignerPanel.ts        | 83 ++++-----------------------------\n src/designer/DesignerPanelFactory.ts | 89 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++\n src/designer/DesignerService.ts      | 26 +++++++++++\n src/designer/MessageHandler.ts       |  3 --\n src/hml/HmlEditorProvider.ts         |  4 +-\n 6 files changed, 127 insertions(+), 79 deletions(-)\n\ncommit 39c9b0be2cffbdef4ff5f16e657b97a396118c27\nAuthor: Developer <user@example.com>\nDate:   Fri Nov 28 07:56:41 2025 +0800\n\n    Refactor: extract WebviewContentProvider and decouple FileManager UI updates\n\n src/designer/DesignerPanel.ts          | 243 ++-------------------------------\n src/designer/FileManager.ts            |  14 +-\n src/designer/WebviewContentProvider.ts | 243 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++\n 3 files changed, 266 insertions(+), 234 deletions(-)\n\ncommit 18735cf1ea2a5146b07cf1b70d914b481add8029\nAuthor: Developer <user@example.com>\nDate:   Fri Nov 28 00:20:33 2025 +0800\n\n    docs: 添加 WebAssembly 真实预览集成方案\n    \n    - 新增需求 R-007: WebAssembly 真实预览集成（产品需求.md）\n    - 新增技术方案文档: WebAssembly集成方案.md\n      - 背景分析：当前 React 模拟渲染的局限性\n      - 技术方案：Emscripten + WebAssembly 编译 HoneyGUI SDK\n      - 架构设计：React 模拟 + Wasm 真实渲染双模式\n      - 实施步骤：4 阶段，预计 14-22 天\n      - 技术难点：OpenGL ES → WebGL 转换、文件系统、内存管理\n      - 成功案例：Figma、AutoCAD Web、Unity WebGL\n    - 更新文档导航（README.md）\n    \n    目标：解决复杂控件（3D、Video、Canvas）无法准确预览的问题\n\n docs/README.md                                     |   3 +\n ...233\\206\\346\\210\\220\\346\\226\\271\\346\\241\\210.md\" | 367 +++++++++++++++++++++\n ...272\\247\\345\\223\\201\\351\\234\\200\\346\\261\\202.md\" |  28 ++\n 3 files changed, 398 insertions(+)\n\ncommit adca22f5d29c92e0ffa4a22ff60062cb46837c3f\nAuthor: Developer <user@example.com>\nDate:   Fri Nov 28 00:19:56 2025 +0800\n\n    refactor(designer): 重构 DesignerPanel 以提升模块化和解耦\n    \n    主要变更：\n    1. 拆分 DesignerPanel.ts 的职责到专用管理类：\n       - AssetManager: 处理资源路径转换、图片选择和重命名\n       - CodeGenManager: 处理代码生成逻辑\n       - ComponentManager: 处理组件的 CRUD 操作\n       - FileManager: 处理 HML 文件的加载、保存和自动保存\n       - MessageHandler: 集中处理 Webview 消息路由\n    \n    2. 优化代码结构：\n       - 实现单一职责原则 (SRP)，降低 DesignerPanel 复杂度\n       - 使用依赖注入方式初始化管理器，提高可测试性\n       - 移除 DesignerPanel 中冗余的私有方法\n       - 统一使用 HmlController 处理 HML 逻辑\n    \n    3. 修复与优化：\n       - 修复图片路径选择逻辑，优先使用项目根目录\n       - 修复组件管理中的类型定义不匹配问题\n       - 确保 Webview 消息处理的类型安全\n\n src/designer/AssetManager.ts     |  374 ++++++++++++\n src/designer/CodeGenManager.ts   |  237 ++++++++\n src/designer/ComponentManager.ts |  115 ++++\n src/designer/DesignerPanel.ts    | 1240 ++------------------------------------\n src/designer/FileManager.ts      |  352 +++++++++++\n src/designer/MessageHandler.ts   |  169 ++++++\n 6 files changed, 1306 insertions(+), 1181 deletions(-)\n\ncommit 73bdad88529383095ba7ca36280d4fdac989e827\nAuthor: Developer <user@example.com>\nDate:   Thu Nov 27 23:21:29 2025 +0800\n\n    refactor: 清理PreviewRunner和SimulationRunner代码\n    \n    - PreviewRunner: 移除废弃的下载功能相关代码和接口定义\n      - 删除 extractZip mock 实现\n      - 删除 RunnerDownloadInfo 接口\n      - 删除 autoDownload 配置选项\n      - 移除 downloadRunner、downloadFile、unzipFile 废弃方法\n      - 简化构造函数配置\n    \n    - SimulationRunner: 修复类型断言问题\n      - 移除不必要的 as any 类型断言\n      - 使用正确的 CodeGenResult 类型访问属性\n\n src/preview/PreviewRunner.ts       | 54 +-------------------------------------\n src/simulation/SimulationRunner.ts |  6 ++---\n 2 files changed, 4 insertions(+), 56 deletions(-)\n\ncommit 3efb2d24ff6f8712a411b98a6cf640725c9d7a04\nAuthor: Developer <user@example.com>\nDate:   Thu Nov 27 23:02:40 2025 +0800\n\n    feat: 架构重构 - 预览与编译仿真分离 (v1.2.0)\n    \n    重大变更：\n    - 预览与编译仿真功能完全分离\n    - 新增 simulation/ 模块实现完整的编译仿真流程\n    - 环境检查、自动编译、仿真运行\n    \n    新增功能：\n    - SimulationService - 编译仿真服务管理\n    - SimulationRunner - 仿真运行器\n    - EnvironmentChecker - 环境检查工具\n    - BuildManager - 编译管理器\n    - SConstructGenerator - 编译脚本生成器\n    - SDK路径三级优先级配置\n    \n    命令变更：\n    - 新增: honeygui.simulation - 启动编译仿真\n    - 新增: honeygui.simulation.stop - 停止编译仿真\n    - 简化: honeygui.preview - 显示开发中提示\n    \n    配置变更：\n    - 新增: honeygui.sdk.path - SDK路径配置\n    - 新增: ProjectConfig.honeyguiSdkPath - 项目级SDK路径\n    \n    文档整理：\n    - 整合架构变更到预览和编译架构.md\n    - 合并代码生成相关文档为代码生成.md\n    - 扁平化docs目录结构\n    - 删除过时文档\n    \n    代码优化：\n    - 修复变量名冲突 (process -> compileProcess)\n    - 移除不必要的类型断言\n    - 修复INTEGRATION.md中的命令名称\n    \n    总计新增约820行代码\n\n CLAUDE.md                                          |  22 +\n ...224\\237\\346\\210\\220\\346\\236\\266\\346\\236\\204.md\" | 539 --------------------\n docs/README.md                                     |  61 +++\n docs/TODO_PROJECT_CONFIG.md                        |  39 --\n ...266\\210\\345\\244\\261\\344\\277\\256\\345\\244\\215.md\" | 163 ------\n ...273\\243\\347\\240\\201\\347\\224\\237\\346\\210\\220.md\" | 273 ++++++++++\n ...275\\277\\347\\224\\250\\347\\244\\272\\344\\276\\213.md\" | 281 -----------\n ...217\\230\\346\\233\\264\\346\\227\\245\\345\\277\\227.md\" |  49 ++\n ...224\\237\\346\\210\\220\\346\\236\\266\\346\\236\\204.md\" |  96 ----\n ...226\\207\\346\\241\\243\\345\\257\\274\\350\\210\\252.md\" |  31 --\n ...225\\264\\347\\220\\206\\350\\257\\264\\346\\230\\216.md\" |  84 ----\n ...274\\226\\350\\257\\221\\346\\236\\266\\346\\236\\204.md\" | 559 ++++++++++++++++++---\n package.json                                       |  20 +-\n src/codegen/honeygui/INTEGRATION.md                |  10 +-\n src/common/ProjectConfig.ts                        |   1 +\n src/common/RunnerStatus.ts                         |  19 +\n src/core/ExtensionManager.ts                       |  10 +-\n src/preview/PreviewService.ts                      | 344 +------------\n src/simulation/BuildManager.ts                     | 204 ++++++++\n src/simulation/EnvironmentChecker.ts               | 132 +++++\n src/simulation/SConstructGenerator.ts              | 107 ++++\n src/simulation/SimulationRunner.ts                 | 213 ++++++++\n src/simulation/SimulationService.ts                | 233 +++++++++\n 23 files changed, 1835 insertions(+), 1655 deletions(-)",
                      "stderr": ""
